title: Arachnifiles

creator: Solo App Lab LLC
descriptionHtml:
Are you an invert enthusiast? Tired of the hassle of keeping track of your inverts in a boring and mundane way? Get ready to be blown away by Arachnifiles - the ultimate app for tracking your creepy crawly companions!

Arachnifiles is not just any tracking app - it's a visually stunning, card-style app that lets you keep track of all your favorite inverts in an interactive way. From Amblypygi to True Spiders, and everything in between, Arachnifiles has got you covered. You can track multiple feeding schedules, molts, substrate changes, and even note your pets' growth rate!

But that's not all! Thanks to our partnership with The Tarantula Collective, Arachnifiles provides access to over 40+ care guides right at your fingertips. And if that's not enough, supporting videos are also available to help you care for your pets like a pro!

Do you have a never-ending wishlist of inverts you want to add to your collection? No worries, Arachnifiles has got you covered! With our wishlist area, you can add and track all the inverts you dream of owning.

So what are you waiting for? Download Arachnifiles today and start tracking your inverts like never before!
descriptionShort: Level up your invert keeping fun with Arachnifiles!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
-New safety measures to ensure you don't overwrite your device data with no cloud backup.
-Moved the account linking from the website and added the account linking in the app.
-Added new info to the Library section! Now the Arachnifiles blog is linked straight to the app so you can see the latest informational posts out there!
-You can now also delete old molt, substrate, and rehouse entries!

-And much more! See release notes in the app from the top right corner of the Homepage in the app!

title:

creator: Solo App Lab LLC
descriptionHtml:
Are you an invert enthusiast? Tired of the hassle of keeping track of your inverts in a boring and mundane way? Get ready to be blown away by Arachnifiles - the ultimate app for tracking your creepy crawly companions!

Arachnifiles is not just any tracking app - it's a visually stunning, card-style app that lets you keep track of all your favorite inverts in an interactive way. From Amblypygi to True Spiders, and everything in between, Arachnifiles has got you covered. You can track multiple feeding schedules, molts, substrate changes, and even note your pets' growth rate!

But that's not all! Thanks to our partnership with The Tarantula Collective, Arachnifiles provides access to over 40+ care guides right at your fingertips. And if that's not enough, supporting videos are also available to help you care for your pets like a pro!

Do you have a never-ending wishlist of inverts you want to add to your collection? No worries, Arachnifiles has got you covered! With our wishlist area, you can add and track all the inverts you dream of owning.

So what are you waiting for? Download Arachnifiles today and start tracking your inverts like never before!
